---
title: Spinach and Toasted Paneer with Basmati Rice
description: Tonight, we're bringing you our lighter version of the traditional 'saag paneer' curry, which pairs delicious Indian cheese (paneer) with spinach and spices. We're opting for heart-healthy olive oil instead of the traditional ghee (clarified butter) for a guilt-free dinner!
